2014年10月22日，[[加拿大|加拿大]][[渥太华|渥太华]][[国会山庄_(加拿大)|国会山庄]]一帶发生数-{zh-hans:起; zh-hant:宗;}-枪击案，枪手迈克尔·扎哈夫-白彼欧杀害在[[加拿大国家战争纪念碑|国家战争纪念碑]]执勤的加拿大軍人内森·西里洛后，闯入有议员正在举行黨團会议的國会大厦，与安保人员驳火<ref name="Nat Post">{{cite news|last1=Multiple|title=Soldier fatally shot outside of Parliament, one gunman killed|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/22/soldier-shot-outside-of-parliament-at-national-war-memorial-active-shooter-believed-to-be-on-the-loose/|accessdate=2014-10-22|publisher=''[[National_Post|National Post]]''|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022195215/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/22/soldier-shot-outside-of-parliament-at-national-war-memorial-active-shooter-believed-to-be-on-the-loose/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/10/22/soldier-shot-at-war-memorial-near-canadian-parliament/|title=Canadian officials identify shooter in brazen attack on Parliament complex|publisher=[[Fox_News_Channel|Fox News Channel]]|accessdate=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022143949/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/10/22/soldier-shot-at-war-memorial-near-canadian-parliament/|archive-date=2014-10-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。事件距[[魁北克|魁北克]][[圣让河畔黎塞留|圣让河畔黎塞留]]士兵遇害案仅两天。

案发后，渥太华市中心核心区域被封锁，警方搜查其他可能的枪手。[[加拿大总理|加拿大总理]][[斯蒂芬·哈珀|斯蒂芬·哈珀]]谴责枪击事件是“野蛮的暴力袭击<ref name="harperspeech"/>”。案件正在由[[皇家加拿大骑警|皇家加拿大骑警]]和其他警察部队调查。

==背景==

案发两天前在圣让河畔黎塞留（Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu），两名加拿大現役軍人被一名25岁男子襲擊。肇事者名为马丁·柯吐尔-鲁洛（Martin Couture-Rouleau），過去多次與警方交涉，2013年皈依为[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]<ref name=suspect/>，並是穆斯林[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]恐怖组织[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]（ISIL）的支持者<ref name=suspect/><ref>{{cite news |work=CBC News |first1=Mark |last1=Gollom |first2=Tracey |last2=Lindeman |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/who-is-martin-couture-rouleau-1.2807285 |title=Who is Martin Couture-Rouleau? |date=2014-10-22 |publisher= |accessdate=2014-10-26 |archive-date=2014-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026063738/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/who-is-martin-couture-rouleau-1.2807285 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。鲁洛用自己的车碾过該两名軍人后[[肇事逃逸|逃逸]]，在追车过程中被警方击毙<ref name=He_seemed>{{cite news|work=National Post|last1=Bell|first1=Stewart|script-title=en:‘He seemed like a typical and fairly boring convert': Inside Martin Rouleau’s rapid descent to extremism|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/21/he-seemed-like-a-typical-and-fairly-boring-convert-inside-martin-rouleaus-rapid-decent-to-extremism/|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022052904/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/21/he-seemed-like-a-typical-and-fairly-boring-convert-inside-martin-rouleaus-rapid-decent-to-extremism/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。52岁的帕特里斯·樊尚（Patrice Vincent）因伤势过重抢救无效死亡<ref name="BBC News"/>。其犯罪动机旨在报复注意自己太多的警方，响应为空袭伊拉克报仇的[[圣战|圣战]]号召<ref name=He_seemed/>。

案发前天，由于樊尚遇害，加之“伊斯兰国和[[基地组织|基地组织]]等激进派在网上不断活跃”，加拿大的恐怖威胁提升至中等级别<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-29722094|title=Canada lifts terror threat level from low to medium|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-22|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022121342/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-29722094|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月22日枪击案发生后，总理哈珀在全国讲话中特别提到了这-{zh-hans:起; zh-hant:宗;}-先前的事件，將之描述為具有ISIL风格的恐怖袭击<ref>{{cite news|last1=CBC news|title=Ottawa shooting: Harper, Mulcair, Trudeau speak about attack|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-harper-mulcair-trudeau-speak-about-attack-1.2809530|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023091350/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-harper-mulcair-trudeau-speak-about-attack-1.2809530|dead-url=no}}</ref>。加拿大皇家骑警证实10月20日和22日的事件没有关联<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bnd.com/2014/10/23/3470864_canadian-police-no-link-between.html?rh=1 |author=Associated Press |title=Canadian police: no link between soldier attacks |date=2014-10-23 |work=BND |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024050638/http://www.bnd.com/2014/10/23/3470864_canadian-police-no-link-between.html?rh=1 |archivedate=2014-10-24 |accessdate=2014-10-24 }}</ref>。

==过程==
===国家战争纪念碑===
[[File:War_monument_(Ottawa).jpg|thumb]]
北美东部时间上午10时前，有人目击到扎哈夫抵达国家战争纪念碑时背着步枪，后来被证实为.30-30口径温彻斯特杠杆式猎枪<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/23/canada-police-ottawa-gunman-video-passport-motive|author=Lauren Gambino|title=Canadian police release video of Ottawa parliament gunman during attack|publisher=''The Guardian''|date=2014-10-24|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025113944/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/23/canada-police-ottawa-gunman-video-passport-motive|dead-url=no}}</ref>。扎哈夫身着蓝色牛仔裤、黑色外套和头巾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/10/22/us-canada-attacks-shooting-idUSKCN0IB1PY20141022|title=Canada's parliament attacked near where prime minister was speaking, Harper safe|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023142053/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/10/22/us-canada-attacks-shooting-idUSKCN0IB1PY20141022|dead-url=no}}</ref>，靠近正在[[无名烈士墓|无名烈士墓]]执勤的阿盖尔和萨瑟兰高地礼仪警卫内森·西里洛下士（Nathan Cirillo），近距离朝背部开出两枪致其重伤<ref name=post-chase>{{cite news |work=National Post |title=RCMP release security footage of Michael Zahef Bibeau during attack, say he shot soldier in back |url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/rcmp-release-security-footage-of-michael-zahef-bibeau-during-attack-say-he-shot-soldier-in-back/ |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-10-24 |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024001132/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/rcmp-release-security-footage-of-michael-zahef-bibeau-during-attack-say-he-shot-soldier-in-back/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。如所有在纪念碑执勤的仪仗队士兵般，西里洛所持的武器没装弹药<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/soldier-shot-at-war-memorial-in-ottawa|title=UPDATE: Day of chaos in the capital leaves soldier and terrorist dead|author=Andrew Duffy|work=Ottawa Citizen|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024143341/http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/soldier-shot-at-war-memorial-in-ottawa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。旁观者立刻抢救西里洛，直至医护人员赶到现场。附近另一名正在执勤礼仪兵，追赶枪手时遭到开枪还击<ref name="post-chase"/>。这名士兵随后回到西里洛的身边<ref>{{cite news |work=CBC News |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/hamilton/news/cpl-nathan-cirillo-s-partner-chased-gunman-military-source-1.2810548 |title=Cpl. Nathan Cirillo's partner chased gunman: military source |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-10-23 |archive-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213043304/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/hamilton/news/cpl-nathan-cirillo-s-partner-chased-gunman-military-source-1.2810548 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

扎哈夫回到他停在纪念碑后威灵顿街南侧的车里，开着车沿着威灵顿街向西行驶，在不远处的国会山庄弃车而逃。经过被分散的围观者后，他翻过国会山庄的栅栏门，劫持了分配给部长的公用车辆，把车开到国会山庄的中央大樓<ref>{{cite news |author=Glen McGregor; David Reevely; Dean Tweed; Dennis Leung |url=https://postmediaottawacitizen2.files.wordpress.com/2014/10/1023shootingupdate-gr.jpg |title=Terror in the Capital |publisher=''Ottawa Citizen'' |date= |accessdate=2014-10-23 |archive-date=2014-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027221701/https://postmediaottawacitizen2.files.wordpress.com/2014/10/1023shootingupdate-gr.jpg |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在国会山巡逻的皇家骑警看见车子被劫后，追逐车子至[[和平塔_(渥太華)|和平塔]]的底部<ref name=post-chase />。

===国会大厦===
[[File:Hall_of_Honour-Centre_Block-Ottawa.jpg|thumb]]
扎哈夫经由和平塔下方的正门进入中央大樓，入口处的下议院当值警员萨恩·桑（Samearn Son）看到扎哈夫手中拿着步枪，立刻冲上前夺枪，使枪口朝地板，并大喊“枪！枪！枪！”。在随后的纠缠中，桑脚部中枪，不得不放开枪手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-s-movements-revealed-by-security-video-1.2810673|title=Ottawa shooting: Michael Zehaf-Bibeau's movements revealed by security video|work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|date=2014-10-23|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024101455/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-s-movements-revealed-by-security-video-1.2810673|dead-url=no}}</ref>。扎哈夫跑下荣誉大厅前往壁龛处的国会图书馆入口时，与警卫交火，双方共开了20-30枪<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-29730956|title=Footage shows bullets fired inside Canada parliament|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023084939/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-29730956|dead-url=no}}</ref>。旁边是加拿大下议院警长凯文·威格士（Kevin Vickers）的办公室。威格士从锁着的箱子拿到一支9毫米手枪后进入大厅。随后他扑倒在地上，朝扎哈夫连开三枪，将其击毙<ref name="CBC live"/><ref name="G&M breaking">{{cite web|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/breaking-news-oct-22/article21217602/|title=Attack on Ottawa: Police in pursuit of multiple shooters|work=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-22|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022203045/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/breaking-news-oct-22/article21217602/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-29747228|title=Ottawa shootings: Video shows security guard Kevin Vickers holding gun|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025163021/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-29747228|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威格士的侄女告诉《卡尔加里太阳报》，这是威格士职业生涯中首次朝别人开枪<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.calgarysun.com/2014/10/22/parliament-hill-shooting-sergeant-at-arms-kevin-vickers-the-family-hero-who-took-down-ottawa-gunman|title=Parliament Hill shooting: Sergeant-At-Arms Kevin Vickers the family hero who took down Ottawa gunman|author=Michael Platt|date=2014-10-22|work=Calgary Sun|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104225103/http://www.calgarysun.com/2014/10/22/parliament-hill-shooting-sergeant-at-arms-kevin-vickers-the-family-hero-who-took-down-ottawa-gunman/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2005年成为下议院职员前，威格士是位杰出的加拿大皇家骑警。

哈珀和[[加拿大官方反对党主席|加拿大官方反对党主席]]、[[加拿大新民主党|新民主党]]领袖[[唐民凯|唐民凯]]当时正在荣誉大厅兩侧的会议室裏與各自的政黨举行[[党团会议|党团会议]]，而下議院第三大黨[[加拿大自由党|自由党]]的党团会议则在楼下举行。保守黨国会议员在会议室大门後築起障礙物，又抓来旗杆用作长矛；哈珀則匿藏在会议室的衣櫃内<ref name=veryproud>{{cite news|last1=CBC News|title=Ottawa shooting: Miramichi 'very proud' of Kevin Vickers|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/ottawa-shooting-miramichi-very-proud-of-kevin-vickers-1.2809944|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024125755/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/ottawa-shooting-miramichi-very-proud-of-kevin-vickers-1.2809944|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Local MP’s talk about the shooting on Parliament Hill|url=http://barrie.ctvnews.ca/local-mp-s-talk-about-the-shooting-on-parliament-hill-1.2065635|accessdate=2014-10-22|publisher=CTV News Barrie|date=2014-10-22|archive-date=2015-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328103551/http://barrie.ctvnews.ca/local-mp-s-talk-about-the-shooting-on-parliament-hill-1.2065635|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Ottawa shooting: N.L. MPs recount chaos moments after gunshots heard|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/newfoundland-labrador/ottawa-shooting-n-l-mps-recount-chaos-moments-after-gunshots-heard-1.2808830|accessdate=2014-10-22|publisher=CBC News|date=2014-10-22|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023114540/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/newfoundland-labrador/ottawa-shooting-n-l-mps-recount-chaos-moments-after-gunshots-heard-1.2808830|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威格士随后向保守党党团解释事发经过，據報向其聲称“我把他擊斃了<ref name=veryproud />”（"I put him down"）或“我曾与嫌疑人交火。他已死亡。”（"I have engaged the suspect. He is deceased."）<ref>{{cite news |work=The Independent |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/ottawa-shooting-sergeantatarms-shot-suspect-at-pointblank-range-after-diving-around-pillar-9818365.html |title=Ottawa shooting: 'Sergeant-at-arms Kevin Vickers shot suspect at point-blank range after diving around pillar' |first=Lizzie |last=Dearden |date=2014-10-25 |accessdate=2014-11-06 |archive-date=2014-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029153159/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/ottawa-shooting-sergeantatarms-shot-suspect-at-pointblank-range-after-diving-around-pillar-9818365.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。案发后，哈珀被疏散至安全地带<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sanchez |first1=Raf |last2=Duggan |first2=Oliver |title=Canadian parliament in lockdown after shooting |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/canada/11180220/Ottawa-shooting-Canadian-parliament-in-lockdown-after-shots-fired.html |accessdate=2014-10-23 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022233932/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/canada/11180220/Ottawa-shooting-Canadian-parliament-in-lockdown-after-shots-fired.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

