迈克尔·扎哈夫-白彼欧<ref name = "LaPresse2310"/><ref name=Guardian/>（Michael Zehaf-Bibeau，1982年10月16日-2014年10月22日）被官方认定为本案的嫌疑犯<ref name=CBS>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/canadian-soldier-shot-at-ottawa-war-memorial/|title=Canadian PM: Ottawa war memorial, Parliament shootings were terrorism|work=CBS News|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-22}}</ref>。[[CBS新闻|CBS新闻]]指称枪手原名迈克尔·约瑟夫·霍尔（Michael Joseph Hall），偶尔称自己阿卜杜勒·扎哈夫-白彼欧（Abdul Zehaf-Bibeau）或是迈克尔·阿卜杜勒·扎哈夫-白彼欧（Michael Abdul Zehaf-Bibeau）<ref name=birth/><ref name=CBS/><ref name=suspect>{{cite news|date=2014-10-22|title=Canada probes Michael Zehaf-Bibeau as possible suspect in Ottawa shooting: source|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/10/22/us-canada-attacks-suspect-idUSKCN0IB2IX20141022|newspaper=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|location=Ottawa|accessdate=2014-10-22|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022234951/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/10/22/us-canada-attacks-suspect-idUSKCN0IB2IX20141022|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据滿地可《新聞报》报道，枪手于1995年13岁时正式将姓氏由霍尔改为扎哈夫-白彼欧<ref name = "LaPresse2310"/><ref name="news.nationalpost.com">{{Cite web |url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/details-of-michael-zehaf-bibeaus-life-paint-a-picture-of-a-man-troubled-by-drugs-and-crime/ |title=Details of Michael Zehaf-Bibeau’s life paint a picture of a man troubled by drugs and crime |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024042550/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/details-of-michael-zehaf-bibeaus-life-paint-a-picture-of-a-man-troubled-by-drugs-and-crime/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/details-of-michael-zehaf-bibeaus-life-paint-a-picture-of-a-man-troubled-by-drugs-and-crime/|title=Ottawa shooter Michael Zehaf-Bibeau was kicked out of mosque|author=Graeme Hamilton, Tristin Hopper, Douglas Todd, Rob Shaw|date=2014-10-23|work=National Post|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024042550/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/details-of-michael-zehaf-bibeaus-life-paint-a-picture-of-a-man-troubled-by-drugs-and-crime/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迈克尔·约瑟夫·霍夫在蒙特利尔北部长大，受到特权阶层的私立教育，然而他十分抵触这种背景。魁北克法院记录显示，枪手至少犯下13起案件<ref name="independent.ie"/>。

====私生活====
扎哈夫-白彼欧在加拿大东部长大，辗转于渥太华和蒙特利尔。在移居加拿大东部过上煤矿工人的生活前，他曾到过利比亚<ref name=freeze />。其母苏珊·白彼欧是蒙特利尔的[[法裔加拿大人|法裔加拿大人]]，加拿大移民及难民局一部门副总管。其养父Bulgasem Zehaf<ref name="cnn.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/22/world/canada-shooter/|title=Who is Michael Zehaf-Bibeau, the man behind the deadly Ottawa attack?|date=2014-10-23|work=CNN|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023173225/http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/22/world/canada-shooter/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|work=The Guardian|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/23/ottawa-shooting-suspect-michael-zehaf-bibeau-canada-parliament/|title=Ottawa shooting suspect Michael Zehaf-Bibeau: what do we know?|date=2014-10-24|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024221803/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/23/ottawa-shooting-suspect-michael-zehaf-bibeau-canada-parliament|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[2011年利比亚内战|2011年利比亚内战]]时移居魁北克，在蒙特利尔开咖啡厅<ref name="Graeme Hamilton, Tristin Hopper, Douglas Todd, Rob Shaw, Peter Henderson">{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/details-of-michael-zehaf-bibeaus-life-paint-a-picture-of-a-man-troubled-by-drugs-and-crime/|title=Ottawa shooter Michael Zehaf-Bibeau was kicked out of mosque|author=Graeme Hamilton, Tristin Hopper, Douglas Todd, Rob Shaw, Peter Henderson|date=2014-10-23|work=National Post|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024042550/http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/23/details-of-michael-zehaf-bibeaus-life-paint-a-picture-of-a-man-troubled-by-drugs-and-crime/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Zehaf和Bibeau于1999年离婚<ref name="cnn.com"/>。

扎哈夫-白彼欧是个惯犯，持有盗窃、藏毒、违规假释等数项罪名，一度被判处多项刑事罪行，其中一项导致其至少被判处监禁60天<ref>{{cite news |work=The Guardian |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/23/ottawa-shooting-suspect-michael-zehaf-bibeau-canada-parliament/ |title=Ottawa shooting suspect Michael Zehaf-Bibeau: what do we know? |date=2014-10-24 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024221803/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/23/ottawa-shooting-suspect-michael-zehaf-bibeau-canada-parliament |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2001年11月，刚满19岁的他，就被判管有虚假信用卡和[[危险驾驶|危险驾驶]]的罪名<ref name="Graeme Hamilton, Tristin Hopper, Douglas Todd, Rob Shaw, Peter Henderson"/>。2004年，他承认藏匿[[大麻|大麻]]和PCP，却没有出席该案于2006年的庭审，直至三年后因认罪而被释放。2011年，他又被指控在温哥华犯下抢劫和恐吓罪<ref name=criminal>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/michael-zehaf-bibeau-slain-ottawa-shooter-had-criminal-record-in-quebec-b-c-1.2809562 |title=Michael Zehaf-Bibeau, slain Ottawa shooter, had criminal record in Quebec, B.C. |publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |date=2014-10-22 |accessdate=2014-10-23 |archive-date=2014-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023091454/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/michael-zehaf-bibeau-slain-ottawa-shooter-had-criminal-record-in-quebec-b-c-1.2809562 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他声称2011年犯下抢劫就是想让自己被禁锢，以戒除毒瘾。精神鉴定证明他适合接受审判<ref name=vsun>{{cite news |url=http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2014/10/22/suspect-in-ottawa-shooting-charged-in-vancouver-in-2011-robbery/ |work=Vancouver Sun |title=Suspect in Ottawa shooting charged in Vancouver in 2011 robbery |date=2014-10-22 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024054740/http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2014/10/22/suspect-in-ottawa-shooting-charged-in-vancouver-in-2011-robbery/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cnn-bibeau">{{cite news |work=CNN |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/22/world/canada-shooter/index.html |title=Who is Michael Zehaf-Bibeau, the man behind the deadly Ottawa attack? |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024205844/http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/22/world/canada-shooter/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

本来信奉[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]的他<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/canada/11183993/Ottawa-gunman-told-fellow-Muslim-convert-the-devil-is-chasing-me.html|title=Ottawa gunman told fellow Muslim convert 'the devil is chasing me'|date=2014-10-23|work=Telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024033212/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/canada/11183993/Ottawa-gunman-told-fellow-Muslim-convert-the-devil-is-chasing-me.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2004年皈依伊斯兰教<ref name="cnn-bibeau"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/22/world/canada-shooter/ |title=Who is Michael Zehaf-Bibeau, the man behind the deadly Ottawa attack? |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023173225/http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/22/world/canada-shooter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成为[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]穆斯林<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/politics/ottawa-gunman-was-disruptive-at-vancouver-area-mosque|title=Ottawa gunman was disruptive at Vancouver-area mosque|author=Glen McGregor More Glen McGregor|work=Ottawa Citizen|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024052053/http://ottawacitizen.com/news/politics/ottawa-gunman-was-disruptive-at-vancouver-area-mosque|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，常出现在[[本拿比|本拿比]]和温哥华的清真寺<ref name=freeze />。一名熟人回忆称，他的行为“飘忽不定”，好像鬼上身，被打扰到的长老要求他不要来清真寺了。熟人都认为他有[[精神病|精神病]]<ref>{{cite news|work=The Age|url=http://www.theage.com.au/world/he-said-the-devil-is-after-him-what-we-know-about-michael-zehafbibeau-20141023-11aljl.html?skin=text-only/|title='He said the devil is after him': What we know about Michael Zehaf-Bibeau|date=2014-10-24|accessdate=2020-09-24|archive-date=2019-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102143022/https://www.theage.com.au/world/he-said-the-devil-is-after-him-what-we-know-about-michael-zehafbibeau-20141023-11aljl.html?skin=text-only%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自10月2日起，他住在靠近国会山庄的渥太华慈善機構（Ottawa Mission）收容所。案发当天，他正就申请[[加拿大护照|加拿大护照]]接受[[背景调查|背景调查]]。皇家骑警专员鲍勃·鲍尔森表示，正是这个问题推动了枪击案的发生<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/ottawa-shooting-suspect-michael-zehaf-bibeau-had-very-developed-criminality-1.2067255|title=Ottawa shooting suspect Michael Zehaf-Bibeau had 'very developed criminality'|publisher=CTV News|date=2014-10-23|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024040410/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/ottawa-shooting-suspect-michael-zehaf-bibeau-had-very-developed-criminality-1.2067255|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管他不在皇家骑警的高危恐怖分子名单上，但与警方所认识的另一个人有关系<ref name="post-chase"/>。按照同伴所言，白彼欧想要回到利比亚学习阿拉伯语和伊斯兰教<ref name="freeze" />。他的母亲告诉警方，他一直想去叙利亚参加[[叙利亚内战|反政府武装组织]]<ref name=suspect/><ref name="news.nationalpost.com"/><ref name="freeze" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/mps-head-back-to-work-morning-after-ottawa-shooting/article21254540/|title=Ottawa suspect tried to get passport to go to Syria|work=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-22|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023183543/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/mps-head-back-to-work-morning-after-ottawa-shooting/article21254540/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/parliament-shooting/article21217602|title=Attack on Ottawa: PM Harper cites terrorist motive|work=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2014-10-22|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022203646/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/parliament-shooting/article21217602/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。皇家骑警称他可能有利比亚国籍<ref name=dm-oct23>{{cite news |work=Daily Mail |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2805054/Mom-Canada-suspect-I-cry-victims-not-son.html |title=Video captures terrifying moment Canadian shooter arrives at Parliament waving a gun while bystanders flee as police reveal he may be a dual citizen with Libya |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023222829/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2805054/Mom-Canada-suspect-I-cry-victims-not-son.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的养父是利比亚人，10月2日申请更换利比亚护照，当天就被拒绝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-wanted-libyan-passport-1.2811768|title=Ottawa shooting: Michael Zehaf-Bibeau wanted Libyan passport|date=2014-10-24|publisher=|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025125213/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-wanted-libyan-passport-1.2811768|dead-url=no}}</ref>。扎哈夫-白彼欧2000年获得利比亚护照后，于2007年前往该国，不料文件过期。他告诉官员更换护照，以探望利比亚的家人和朋友的要求<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-wanted-libyan-passport-1.2811768 |title=Ottawa shooting: Michael Zehaf-Bibeau wanted Libyan passport |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025125213/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-wanted-libyan-passport-1.2811768 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====案发前====
收容所的其他人目击到扎哈夫跟两名男子上了车。其他人感觉这三人“贼眉鼠眼”地打量着周围的一切<ref name="mission">{{cite news |work=Ottawa Citizen |title=Shooter Zehaf-Bibeau was staying at Ottawa Mission before rampage: witnesses |url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/shooter-zehaf-bibeau-was-staying-at-ottawa-mission-before-rampage-witnesses |first=David |last=Henderson |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025170238/http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/shooter-zehaf-bibeau-was-staying-at-ottawa-mission-before-rampage-witnesses |dead-url=no }}</ref>。扎哈夫的车子是在案发前一日购买的<ref name="post-chase"/>。收容所的一位居民表示，案发前三日扎哈夫性情大变，又犯毒瘾。扎哈夫报告其他人自己仇视加拿大，不断为世界末日祈祷<ref>{{cite news |work=CBC News |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-not-among-90-being-probed-rcmp-say-1.2810113 |title=Ottawa shooting: Michael Zehaf-Bibeau not among 90 being probed, RCMP say |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025015359/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-michael-zehaf-bibeau-not-among-90-being-probed-rcmp-say-1.2810113 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====收购武器====
案发时，扎哈夫被法律禁止持有或购得枪支。此外，他有过刑事指控和罪行，有滥药史，没有固定的住址，这些都阻止他获得持枪证<ref name=GunControlFailure/>。据推测他在黑市上偷或买到用来作案的步枪，或是从不知道他的动机或自己是共犯的人那收购步枪<ref name=GunControlFailure/>。

==调查==
[[渥太华警察局|渥太华警察局]]原本负责调查国家战争纪念碑的枪击案，而皇家骑警則负责调查中央大樓的枪击案<ref name="G&M breaking" />。不过，10月23日，渥太华警察局宣布案件事关国家安全，将整个调查移交给皇家骑警。另一方面，加拿大皇家骑警則委托[[安大略省警察局|安大略省警察局]]，就警察和安全部队对事件的反应作独立的标准调查<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-rcmp-takes-over-investigation-opp-to-probe-police-conduct-1.2813339 |title=Ottawa shooting: RCMP takes over investigation, OPP to probe police conduct |publisher=CBC News |date=2014-10-25 |accessdate=2014-11-02 |archive-date=2014-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028045046/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ottawa-shooting-rcmp-takes-over-investigation-opp-to-probe-police-conduct-1.2813339 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=OPP to lead independent probe of Parliament Hill security|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/opp-to-lead-independent-probe-of-parliament-hill-security-1.2071640|accessdate=2014-10-26|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912032226/https://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/gunman-prepared-video-prior-to-ottawa-attack-1.2071640|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月23日，加拿大皇家骑警发布了国会山庄的安全摄像头视频录影，表示扎哈夫进入国会山庄区域后，劫走部长级别的车辆，驾车驶向和平塔入口。他们还表示，扎哈夫-白彼欧不属于皇家骑警高风险旅客名单上的93名可疑恐怖分子。“加拿大皇家骑警在那时候不具备这些信息，担心会泄露有关国家安全的犯罪。”皇家骑警总管保尔逊还宣布，扎哈夫护照的背景审查已展开，在一位被控以恐怖主义罪行的匿名人士的计算机中，发现了扎哈夫的电邮<ref>{{cite news |work=CTV News |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/rcmp-show-dramatic-security-video-of-gunman-behind-ottawa-shootings-1.2068134 |title=RCMP show dramatic security video of gunman behind Ottawa shootings |first=Andrea |last=Janus |date=2014-10-23 |accessdate=2014-11-02 |archive-date=2014-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030141013/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/rcmp-show-dramatic-security-video-of-gunman-behind-ottawa-shootings-1.2068134 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在这次会议上，保尔逊还表示，扎哈夫的母亲告诉警方，他希望去叙利亚，但她后来在接受录影访谈时否认了这一说法，称自己告诉警方他想去的是[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]。

10月26日，加拿大皇家骑警宣布，已有“说服力的证据”表明扎哈夫受“思想政治动机驱使”策划袭击。他们表示，扎哈夫在袭击前曾录过视频。皇家骑警总监保尔逊表示：“他很故意也很清醒得非常有意义的阐述了他行为基础。（他的行为）广泛地是針对加拿大的外交政策和他的宗教信仰”。皇家骑警正在研究“情报和证据的价值”，并未公布录像。但保尔逊表示，希望最终将其发布。

10月27日，皇家骑警总监保尔逊出席國會一個委员会的会议，向国会议员简述调查进展。“尽管我们国家面临着这一威胁，但我们必须集中精力，防范出国旅游的个人犯下恐怖行为。防范这些人出国是至关重要的。如果这些人受到训练、带着战斗经验回来，他们会给本国和我们的盟友，带来更大的威胁<ref name=reuters-oct27>{{cite news |last1=Palmer |first1=Randall |title=Canada must do more to rein in threat from radicals: police head |url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKBN0IF0OE20141027?pageNumber=2&virtualBrandChannel=0 |accessdate=2014-10-27 |work=Reuters |date=2014-10-27 |language=en |first2=David |last2=Ljunggren |first3=Richard |last3=Valdmanis |archive-date=2014-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030095647/http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKBN0IF0OE20141027?pageNumber=2&virtualBrandChannel=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

加拿大政府原本計劃在國會推出一项法案，拓宽间谍机构[[加拿大安全情报局|加拿大安全情报局]]的權力，但受枪击案影响而推迟至10月27日出台。該法案會允许情报局在國外行動，並允許該局引入计划，對因從事恐怖活動而定罪的双重国籍人士撤销其加拿大公民身份<ref name=reuters-oct27/>。

